overview: Comedy special by Comedian Zoltan Kaszas, known for his Dry Bar Comedy Special "Cat Jokes" (2017) and "Modern Male" (2020) this hour was filmed in February of 2016 at Comedy Underground in Seattle, Washington. This was filmed during one of the late shows I did that weekend so the crowd is a little drunk, a little rowdy but a lot of fun!
title: Zoltan Kaszas: Dancin' With Drunks
